# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene5.rpy:51
translate chinese u19a2s5_db4e93dd:

    # "Second Bandit" "Just kill him and take his shit!"
    "Second Bandit" "干脆杀了他，抢走他的东西！"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene5.rpy:52
translate chinese u19a2s5_dee6a366:

    # "I grab my sword and jump to my feet just before they are on me."
    "就在他们扑上来之前，我抓起剑猛地站起身。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene5.rpy:78
translate chinese u19a2s5b_2026aad1:

    # gg "Damn, I'm glad I heard them. That could have been bad."
    gg "该死，幸好我听到了动静。那可就糟了。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene5.rpy:80
translate chinese u19a2s5b_5f3e99eb:

    # sg "Good thing they were noisy and I heard them coming."
    sg "幸好他们动静太大，我听到了他们过来的声音。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene5.rpy:82
translate chinese u19a2s5b_4c4ed9ab:

    # bn "Luckily I heard them coming. I was up reading, because I couldn't sleep."
    bn "幸好我听到了他们过来的声音。我本来正因为睡不着而在看书。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene5.rpy:84
translate chinese u19a2s5b_4ae383e5:

    # sst "That was close. I almost didn't hear them from the river."
    sst "好险。我差点没听到他们从河边过来的声音。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene5.rpy:86
translate chinese u19a2s5b_98efddd3:

    # rb "What is with these guys!? Ugh!"
    rb "这些家伙到底怎么回事！？呸！"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene5.rpy:88
translate chinese u19a2s5b_46bbbfd8:

    # cw "That was too close. I'm glad I heard them approaching."
    cw "太危险了。幸好我听到了他们靠近的声音。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene5.rpy:90
translate chinese u19a2s5b_ac9b0b42:

    # "Lucky they woke me. Otherwise, they could have just slit my throat in my sleep."
    "幸好他们把我吵醒了。不然，他们说不定就在我睡着的时候割断我的喉咙。"

