translate chinese u19a2s5b_ca22d961:

    # "I don't think I'll be getting any more sleep tonight. Might as well just stay up and tend to the fire."
    "我觉得今晚睡不着了。不如干脆起来照看火堆。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene5.rpy:125
